stallData.name: Jin Hua Mixed Veg Rice
stallData.htmlDescription:
Opening Hours
9.30am - 7.30pm. Rest day random

Dishes
Economical Rice Cai Fan

Description
Good and cheap cai fan. Very home-cooked style, run by uncle and auntie and their son. Somedays their dishes can be amazing when the chef feels like it. A staple in Ghim Moh market, would recommend it for the unique taste profile

Price
$3 - $5

Favorites
Cabbage, Minced Pork

location.name: Ghim Moh Market and Hawker Centre
